The paper deals with the approximation of submodular functions, which is a fundamental object of study in combinatorial optimization, economics, and machine learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
